g Cards","id":29},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":268030,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Digital Deluxe Edition</h1><p>The Digital Deluxe Edition features:<br>- Digital 40 page &quot;Extended Manual&quot; with advanced tactics and background info (PDF)<br>- Digital 80 page &quot;Weapon's manual&quot; with &quot;tips &amp; tricks&quot; for every unit (PDF)<br>- Digital soundtrack, featuring 10 tracks (all original compositions)</p><br><h1>Steam Greenlight</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/237470/extras/greenlight.png?t=1725014383\" /><br><br>Thanks to everybody who helped us getting the Greenlight in less than 14 days!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Battle Worlds: Kronos is a classic turn-based strategy game in the tradition of <strong>Battle Isle</strong>, <strong>Advance Wars</strong> and <strong>Panzer General</strong>. Have you ever wondered what games like that would look like today? Well, we did. As a result, we decided to develope Battle Worlds: Kronos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Two Single Player Campaigns</strong> (~50 hours of gameplay)<br></li><li><strong>Single Player Challenge Maps</strong> - Test your skills in different combat scenarios and keep track of your progress. <br></li><li><strong>Live Multiplayer</strong> - Battle your friends live on the internet (cross-platform) or via hot-seat.<br></li><li><strong>Asynchronous Multiplayer</strong> - Take all the time you need and consider your moves. Similar to &quot;play-by-mail&quot;, your round is stored on our server and turned over to your opponent. The system allows you to continue the match anytime and anywhere you want (cross-platform).<br></li><li><strong>Online Features</strong> - Leagues, chat and - in early 2014 - tournaments.<br></li><li><strong>Strong AI</strong> - A clever AI that will challenge even experienced commanders.<br></li><li><strong>Map Editor</strong> - A powerful editor to create your own maps and missions (Windows only).<br></li><li><strong>Includes &quot;Trains&quot; DLC</strong> - Additional ~15 hours campaign, new units and new multiplayer maps</li></ul>","developers":["KING Art"],"genres":[{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/237470/header.jpg?t=1725014383","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"Battle Worlds: Kronos \u00a9 2013 KING Art GmbH. All rights reserved.<br />\r\nWe assume no liability for damage caused by possible viruses. All brand names and trademarks are property of their respective owners.","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 12.04 LTS or newer<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 Ghz Dual-Core<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> OpenGL 2.1, GeForce GTX 260 or better, proprietary driver recommended<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 3 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> Integrated audio interface<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Might work on other Linux distributions as well (see Forum)</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Mac OS 10.6 (Snow Leopard) or newer<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 Ghz Dual-Core<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> OpenGL 2.1, Intel HD Graphics 4000 or better<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 3 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> Integrated audio interface</li></ul>"},"metacritic":{"score":71,"url":"https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/battle-worlds-kronos?ftag=MCD-06-10aaa1f"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":2030010,"mp4":{"480":"http://